<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Feedback Enviado!</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @keyframes popIn {
            0% { transform: scale(0.6); opacity: 0; }
            70% { transform: scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }
        .animate-pop { animation: popIn 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen text-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-100 max-w-sm w-full border border-slate-100 animate-pop">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-emerald-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm border border-emerald-100 animate-pulse">
            <span class="text-4xl">🎉</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Tudo certo!</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-8 px-2">Obrigado por compartilhar seu momento conosco. Sua voz faz a diferença.</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="block w-full bg-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold py-3.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition text-sm shadow-md shadow-indigo-100">
                Ver Meu Histórico
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="block w-full text-slate-500 font-medium py-2 rounded-xl hover:text-slate-700 text-xs transition">
                Fazer Nova Submissão
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>